<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="opponent-n">opponent <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ə'pəʊnənt/    美 /ə'poʊnənt/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>对手；反对者</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My opponent was much older than I.
我的对手年龄比我大得多。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Opponents of factory farming say that it is cruel to the animals.
工厂化养殖的反对者说这对动物很残忍。</p><footer>北师大新选必① – 3</footer></div></div>